  MAN command|errno

This command provides an environment
for displaying manual pages - small
documentation files - for commands and
programs. It can also show short
descriptions of error numbers.

Press any key to view the next page.
<ESC> or <BREAK> will stop the display
of the current manual page.

Special manual pages:
  HELP       - short description
  COMMANDS   - list of commands
  ERRORS     - list of error codes
